    "wizard_grade_option": "Hitamo iki urwego rw'ishuri kuri cyawe isomo. Determines amagambo na concept ubukomere.",
    "wizard_growth_goal_input": "Injiza learning growth intego kuri umunyeshuri ku achieve hamwe na iki ibirimo.",
    "wizard_instructions_input": "Ongeraho gakondo amabwiriza kuri AI ku follow igihe kurema isomo ibirimo.",
